HEADWORD: Wolfsbane
<hw>Wolfs"bane`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Bot.)</fld>
<def>A poisonous plant (<spn>Aconitum Lycoctonum</spn>), a kind of
monkshood; also, by extension, any plant or species of the genus
<gen>Aconitum</gen>. See <er>Aconite</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Wolf's-claw</ent>⟦br⟧
